urreição</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note4c\" data-full-marker=\"4c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168950\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.51-55?lang=por#p51\">1 Cor. 15:51–55</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"d\" id=\"note4d\" data-full-marker=\"4d\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168952\" id=\"note4d_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/eternal-life?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Vida eterna</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"7\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note7a\" data-full-marker=\"7a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168954\" id=\"note7a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.50-70?lang=por#p50\">D&amp;C 76:50–70</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note7b\" data-full-marker=\"7b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168955\" id=\"note7b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.26?lang=por#p26\">2 Né. 2:26</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.27?lang=por#p27\">Al. 42:27</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/14.30?lang=por#p30\">Hel. 14:30</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/agency?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Arbítrio</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"8\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note8a\" data-full-marker=\"8a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168957\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.38?lang=por#p38\">D&amp;C 1:38</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"9\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note9a\" data-full-marker=\"9a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168959\" id=\"note9a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.23-28?lang=por#p23\">D&amp;C 42:23–28</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"10\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\